er Rougier-Lagane\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"UGA)Achraf Ed Doghmy\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2727}, {\"ngram\": \"MOR\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"+1'33\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"the break\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"peloton\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a brilliant view at the start.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a brilliant view\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Achraf Ed Doghmy (MOR) All that effort to get into the breakaway and now he is out of the back again as he is unable to fix it with his car behind the peloton and neutral service are not able to help either.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Achraf Ed Doghmy\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"MOR\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"All that effort\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakaway\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"his car\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton and neutral service\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lots of the big favourites are sitting near the back.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lots\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"the big favourites\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mathieu van der Poel (NED) riding a golden Canyon today.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9225263441329685, \"rank\": 0.0767926218628998, \"text\": \"NED\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mathieu van der\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden Canyon\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is not the only one, though.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pinarello riders have a gold and black frame to ride.\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pinarello riders\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold and black frame\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quick chat with the Dutch national head coach, Koos Moerenhout by Laura Weislo: Tell me what you think about the race today.\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3257, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9390179839014496, \"rank\": 0.06427425365296453, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3284, \"end\": 3299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koos_Moerenhout\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Koos Moerenhout\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koos_Moerenhout\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koos_Moerenhout\"}, {\"begin\": 3303, \"end\": 3308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9776757842860636, \"rank\": 0.01259334026246262, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Interesting, long, quite open.\\\"\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Says Moerenhout.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Moerenhout\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I think there are many possibilities for tactics and also different riders maybe you do not expect.\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many possibilities\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"tactics\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"also different riders\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So we will see.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I know with such a small peloton that it's going to be a very different dynamic.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a small peloton\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"a very different dynamic\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, there are many more possibilities at the start of the race.\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many more possibilities\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us say it like that.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the end, I think also the big teams will try to have a focus on each other.\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"the big teams\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There might be not that big of a difference, but at one point, for sure, it will, and especially the small size of the peloton, and also, in combination with no communication, basically, is makes it interesting.\\\"\", \"from\": 3798, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3860}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the small size\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3910}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"combination\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"no communication\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is the final climb steep like in Glasgow's Worlds route last year?\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4046, \"end\": 4053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9874384382135567, \"rank\": 0.012059536352488825, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final climb\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not, I do not think so, but it's the repetition.\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the repetition\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the repetition of the climbs during the day, which will make it hard, compared with the distance 275k it's like monumental so not everybody, is capable of doing that and be as fit in the final as some guys can, or at least prove to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the repetition\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4155}, {\"ngram\": \"the climbs\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4177, \"to\": 4184}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4237}, {\"ngram\": \"not everybody\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"some guys\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a hard day... A day for Mathieu van der Poel?\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4408, \"end\": 4428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathieu van der Poel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard day\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"A day\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will see you never know.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Preparation has been good.\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Preparation\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He loves this kind of racing and that's good to start with, but in the end, the race has to be ridden.\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4505}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4515}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4561}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His level is good, but there are more riders whose level are good as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His level\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"more riders\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"whose level\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch and Danish riders are riding at a pretty solid tempo at the front of the peloton for Van der Poel and Pedersen.\", \"from\": 4669, \"to\": 4790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4673, \"end\": 4678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.7157395366770646, \"rank\": 0.2930464080011536, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4683, \"end\": 4689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.7554545125367833, \"rank\": 0.23294838018040698, \"text\": \"Danish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pretty solid tempo\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4731}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4744}, {\"ngram\": \"the peloton\", \"from\": 4748, \"to\": 4759}, {\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 4764, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"Pedersen\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, South Africa's Ryan Gibbons is up there too as he is trade teammates with Pedersen so will likely ride for him.\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4797, \"end\": 4809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9865895713607762, \"rank\": 0.010096612153364453, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gibbons_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9846123071127694, \"rank\": 0.015624999999999825, \"text\": \"Ryan Gibbons\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gibbons_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Gibbons_(cyclist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trade teammates\", \"from\": 4850, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"Pedersen\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ed Doghmy (Mor) is just 30 seconds behind the breakaway.\", \"from\": 4910, \"to\": 4966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ed Doghmy\", \"from\": 4910, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"Mor\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4924}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakaway\", \"from\": 4952, \"to\": 4965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The leaders now have over seven minutes on the Danish led pack.\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 5030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5014, \"end\": 5020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danish_language\", \"score\": 0.9821858113391515, \"rank\": 0.01384509763152082, \"text\": \"Danish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danish_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The leaders\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4978}, {\"ngram\": \"over seven minutes\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Weislo had a chat with Mads Pedersen before the start today.\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5032, \"end\": 5037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.5482841507147602, \"rank\": 0.4758428597387613, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 5061, \"end\": 5074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9973584045700955, \"rank\": 0.0026481297583581327, \"text\": \"Mads Pedersen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mads_Pedersen_(cyclist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chat\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5055}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q: What do you think about the course today?\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Q\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's pretty good.\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The National coach saw it a long time ago, and he thinks it fits me really well, and so do I.\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The National coach\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am pretty happy with it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Q: You have got a strong team around you today.\", \"from\": 5291, \"to\": 5338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong team\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who do you think that you are going to be looking at today in the in the race, \\\"Mainly we will focus on our own race.\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 5392, \"to\": 5397}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5416}, {\"ngram\": \"our own race\", \"from\": 5443, \"to\": 5455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's the most important if you, if you look too much at other teams, you will always be one step behind.\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other teams\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we keep our own focus and focusing on racing our race.\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our own focus\", \"from\": 5584, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"our race\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But of course, the Belgium, Dutchies and Great Britain.\", \"from\": 5631, \"to\": 5686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5672, \"end\": 5685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6373328220868335, \"rank\": 0.32571379236314685, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5638, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"Dutchies\", \"from\": 5659, \"to\": 5667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for sure, some smaller teams we have to look out for.\\\"\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And for sure, some smaller teams\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Q:What do you think about this small peloton?\", \"from\": 5747, \"to\": 5792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Q\", \"from\": 5747, \"to\": 5748}, {\"ngram\": \"this small peloton\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it is what it is.\", \"from\": 5794, \"to\": 5820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, it would have been nice to be eight guys here, of course.\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight guys\", \"from\": 5861, \"to\": 5871}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 5887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the rules is, it's like it is, and we just get the best out of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are well over 200km to the finish.\", \"from\": 5964, \"to\": 6001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"well over 200km\", \"from\": 5971, \"to\": 5986}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the longest ever Olympic road race on what should be a brilliantly exciting course.\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the longest ever Olympic road race\", \"from\": 6010, \"to\": 6044}, {\"ngram\": \"a brilliantly exciting course\", \"from\": 6063, \"to\": 6092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel (NED) now has moved himself up to fourth wheel in the peloton.\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6109, \"end\": 6112, \"titl